{"tid":1118118,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"無限係一個咩概念？","createTime":"2019-04-21T07:37:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-21T11:04:01.000Z","uid":137088,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e9b95fa3bf9fff82eb986b891f41c29ad4e556f0","tid":1118118,"uid":137088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T07:37:56.000Z","msg":"點理解無限？<br />\n無限定無限＋1大？？？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60ff90c1f76be67be59061bccd50561caa08a3c9","tid":1118118,"uid":245399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T07:49:23.000Z","msg":"簡單咁講，無限就係不停以某種方式延續。"},{"pid":"0b34e39daefa6b287bce7fd1660682dfb008bcff","tid":1118118,"uid":245399,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T08:23:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點理解無限？<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">無限定無限＋1大？？？</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實好難就咁答你，無限同無限有好多種嘅比較方式。<br />\n擧例咁講,你當係有兩個數 x 同 y , 佢地都越黎越大,唔停嗰隻, 咁佢地都趨向咗無限大.你應該係想問:「咁 x 同 y 邊個大啲?」<br />\n但係 x 同 y 趨向無限大嘅速度會影響結果, 你可以想像吓 個x大得快好多好多,個y大得慢啲但都會不斷變大, 咁最終就可能係x&gt;y.<br />\n<br />\n例1: x 同 y 比 , y=x+1 , 當x趨向無限大, 最終一樣大<br />\n例2: 都係 x 同 y 比,今次 y=x^2 , 當x趨向無限大, 最終 y&gt;x<br />\n<br />\n唔明再問"},{"pid":"706088a09a7c88690904566459f8d18175bb328b","tid":1118118,"uid":245399,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T08:37:38.000Z","msg":"另一種玩法:<br />\n比如有一條直直嘅街道，一邊無限延長。<br />\n街道有兩側，其中一側每1米1棵樹，另一側每2米1棵樹，如下圖，比較兩側的樹。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/35b72SA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F35b72SA.png&h=e214c258&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n畀編號佢地，發覺其實都係同一種數法，所以冇一邊比另一邊多<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0rbG7jf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0rbG7jf.png&h=37a1f401&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e977ee92dfa06ade6ba888cb262602dcd6e60fd9","tid":1118118,"uid":242626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T08:45:49.000Z","msg":"有種叫surreal numbers嘅玩法<br />\n係專去表達無限大+1嘅數"},{"pid":"10ed8004b37af5dbaebee4079c3a24707b9e2e2d","tid":1118118,"uid":245399,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e977ee92dfa06ade6ba888cb262602dcd6e60fd9","tid":1118118,"uid":242626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T08:45:49.000Z","msg":"有種叫surreal numbers嘅玩法<br />\n係專去表達無限大+1嘅數"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T08:56:35.000Z","msg":"中文嘅同學叫《超現實數》<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f385a14e35bc939820daf065db69ab1593f81f7f","tid":1118118,"uid":3441,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e977ee92dfa06ade6ba888cb262602dcd6e60fd9","tid":1118118,"uid":242626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T08:45:49.000Z","msg":"有種叫surreal numbers嘅玩法<br />\n係專去表達無限大+1嘅數"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T08:59:39.000Z","msg":"not exactly. Surreals number is one of the approach to take infinity and infinitestimal quantities in a mathematically rigorous setting."},{"pid":"859061704ad519427ae33d0d5fab93cd0d93336c","tid":1118118,"uid":152636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T10:00:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/SrU9YDoXE88\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FSrU9YDoXE88&d=CcUT5H46krin9iWjsTG5RPch229KM6nXCMtlUoiobV8%3D&h=9cc72c9c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/SrU9YDoXE88</a>"},{"pid":"f58ee7db5c01ed5ce3ad30e9ed029c2c268bd0d8","tid":1118118,"uid":137088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T10:07:09.000Z","msg":"無限點解可以＋1<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4eb2806a36cd11fb13c6539e4fac255ca0f8ee09","tid":1118118,"uid":38518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f58ee7db5c01ed5ce3ad30e9ed029c2c268bd0d8","tid":1118118,"uid":137088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"